<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="praise-n">praise <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'preɪz/    美 /'preɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U]赞扬；表扬：</strong></h4>
<p>反 criticism </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be worthy of / deserve praise 
值得称赞</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The film has <strong>won high praise from</strong> general audiences. 
这部影片得到了所有观众的高度赞扬。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-praise-of">in praise of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>赞扬：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She wrote a poem in praise of freedom. 
她写了一首诗歌颂自由。</p></div></div>